3 (4) "Covered clinical project" means an industry-sponsored, interventional
4 clinical trial involving a drug, biologic, or medical device regulated by the United
5 States Food and Drug Administration and conducted at a site located in this state,
6 including early-phase, first-in-human, dose-escalation, proof-of-concept,
7 precision-medicine, rare-disease, cell-therapy, gene-therapy, biologic, or
